Responsibilities
Responsibilities:Promote and sell a wide range of 3M Traffic Safety & Security products, like reflective sheets.Develop, maintain and enhance customer relationships.Work with distributors to maximize sales coverage and to provide better customer service. Requirements:Possesses a Bachelor's or Master's degree in Civil Engineering.Has at least 4 years of business-to-business (B2B) sales experience in the industrial manufacturing or traffic safety industry.Has a good command of English, both verbal and written.Result-oriented, self-driven, aggressive and highly motivated. A fast learner with good analytical thinking.
